      "span_text": "The Norwegian study evaluated consumers' perceptions of the POS display ban implemented in January 2010.  Around a quarter of smokers reported being tempted to buy tobacco when exposed to POS displays prelegislation, and most agreed the ban would make smoking uptake more difficult.",
